deposit_typeNon Refund	285	Dominant driver; extremely high risk of cancellation
total_of_special_requests	0.49	Protective; each request halves odds of cancellation
hotelResort	0.82	Protective; 18% lower odds than City Hotels
lead_time	1.004	Risk; longer lead time slightly increases odds
